 wizard starts dispelling himself, he'll dispell his own epic. By the way, do you realize that Vexing is a dot and not a DD? That's right -- eats right through their epic.</P><P>Mage epic -- a joke.</P><P><hr height=1 noshade id=quote></BLOCKQUOTE id=quote></font id=quote><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size=2 id=quote></P><P>Ok Mr Rocket Scientist, how do you know which buffs slot a Wizard epic's effect is in? The Mage epic is a joke? No youre the only joke.</P><P><BR><BLOCKQUOTE id=quote><font size=1 face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" id=quote>quote:<hr height=1 noshade id=quote>quote:<BR>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<BR>Uhh, what melee is going to be stupid enough to dispell Heat Blood? 2/3 of 75dmg, wow that's going to take a chunk of hp out of them!<BR>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------</P><P><BR>They are not going to check what dot you land on them each time, chances are they will dispell after each time you land a dot. This is a good way to get rid of those pumice charges.</P><P><hr height=1 noshade id=quote></BLOCKQUOTE id=quote></font id=quote><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size=2 id=quote> </P><P>WTF are you even talking about? It's amazing how you can get into peoples minds once again to know what they are thinking.</P><P></P><P><BLOCKQUOTE id=quote><font size=1 face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" id=quote>quote:<hr height=1 noshade id=quote>quote:<BR>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<BR>it lowers your MAGIC RESIST. This allows you to get ROOTED. ROOT = DEAD.<BR>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------</P><P><BR>Wow did your account get hacked and all your gear stolen? If you are capable of getting rooted after malo you are one pathetically equipped character. As to the poison debuff, SO WHAT? You realize that we have something called Vexing and ToN, right? Oh, how